headline.print_headline: Auditor Finds Discrepancy in Kabel Deutschland Takeover Price
headline.main: Auditor Finds Discrepancy in Kabel Deutschland Takeover Price

lead_paragraph: A special auditor's report concluded there was a discrepancy between the price paid for German cable firm Kabel Deutschland by Britain's Vodafone and the value of the company.
